### Create classroom - happy path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Sunflower Room",
  "ageGroup": 0
}

### Create classroom - duplicate name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Sunflower Room",
  "ageGroup": 1
}

### Create classroom - validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "AB",
  "ageGroup": 0
}

### Get all classrooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get classroom by ID - replace with actual ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get classroom by ID - not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update classroom
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Rainbow Room"
}

### Delete classroom
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### No token - expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms

### Teacher token on POST - expect 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

{
  "name": "Blue Room",
  "ageGroup": 0
}